skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: tough mudder countdown
des: Tough Mudder is great but don't lose sight of how many days you have left to train and get ready! Open the skill and Alexa will automatically tell you how many days remain until all your upcoming Tough Mudder challenge. Alexa can also remind you about the exact date for a specific events.
priv: Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
